==English==

===Verb===
'''cheers'''

# 3nd person singular present simple of ''to [[cheer]]''.

===Noun===
'''cheers'''

# plural of ''[[cheer]]''.

===Interjection===
'''cheers!'''

# the usual [[toast]] when drinking alcohol
# "[[thanks]]"
# {{informal}} [[goodbye]], [[bye]]

====Synonyms====
*[[bottoms up]]

